"{\"uid\": \"standard.co.uk-sport-sport-olympics-paris-olympics-2024-swimming-schedule-uk-start-time-dates-b1172066.html\", \"text\": \"To use the search feature, we need your consent to load Google Custom Search, which may use cookies or similar technologies. Please click 'Allow and Continue' below to enable search. See our privacy policy for more information.  Sport|Olympics  The pool will be one of the star attractions at the 2024 ParisOlympicsas theswimmingaction gets underway.  Team GBhopes are high althoughAdam Peatyfaces a big challenge in his battle to retain his 100m breaststroke gold with China's Qin Haiyang the favourite this time around.  The target is to beat the eight medals won at the lastOlympic Gamesand top of their wishlist is the 4x200m men's freestyle relay, a title which GB will be defending.Ben Proudis another hopeful, in the 50m freestyle.  Once again, eyes will be onKatie Ledeckyas the most successful female swimmer in history. Ariarne Titmus won gold in the 400m freestyle for Australia in Tokyo and Canadian teenager Summer McIntosh is also aiming for victory in what should be an enthralling event.  As for home favourites, France will be backing multiple world champion Leon Marchand to the hilt.  ThroughoutParis 2024, swimming events are to be split between morning and evening sessions at Paris La Defense Arena.  Here is the full 2024 Olympics swimming schedule (all times BST)...  10:00  19:30Women's 100m Butterfly - Semifinals  19:42Men's 400m Freestyle - Final  19:52Women's 400m Freestyle - Final  20:12Men's 100m Breaststroke - Semifinals  20:34Women's 4x100m Freestyle Relay - Final  20:44Men's 4x100m Freestyle Relay - Final  10:00  19:30Men's 400m Medley - Final  19:40Women's 100m Butterfly - Final  19:46Men's 200m Freestyle - Semifinals  20:10Women's 100m Breaststroke - Semifinals  20:32Men's 100m Backstroke - Semifinals  20:44Men's 100m Breaststroke - Final  20:50Women's 200m Freestyle - Semifinals  10:00  19:30Women's 400m Medley - Fina